>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1499.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.phantommessenger.com/bamfort/pooh-zen.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Damage Bonus question</span><hr size=1> Once your damage bonus kicks in (lvl 28 - the formula is [level minus 25 times 3]), every time you hit with your main hand (using h2h or 1hb), you will get that amount added to the hit. The bonus will go up by 1 every 3 levels.  That is why you want the fastest weapon in your main hand...so you get that extra damage as often as possible.<br>
<br>
As for 2hb, I'm still not sure how that works<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ...there are variables based on the speed of the weapon - a slower weapon gets a better bonus.<br>
<br>
It doesn't increase the damage of the weapon (i.e. a 8/20 weapon will not become a 11/20 at lvl 34), you just get an extra 3 points every time you hit.<br>
<br>
And the bonus listed on a weapon is what your bonus is at what ever level you are.  So, if you give the weapon to someone 3 levels lower than you, the bonus will show (for them) 1 point less than it does for you. <p><center><table border=0><tr><td valign=bottom align=right width=200 bgcolor="#778899"><b><a href="http://www.phantommessenger.com/bamfort/"><font size="-1" color="#8b1a1a" face="comic sans ms">Bamfort Maldwitt</font></a></b><br><b><font color="#003366">Monk of the Ashen Order</font></b></td><td rowspan=2 align=middle valign=middle bgcolor="#000000"><img src="http://www.phantommessenger.com/bamfort/kungfu8.jpg"></td><td bgcolor="#778899" valign=bottom align=left width=200><b><font color="#003366">51st Koan of Meditation</font></b><br><font size="-1" color="#8b1a1a" face="comic sans ms"><b>Bristlebane</b></font></td></tr><tr><td align=right bgcolor="#778899"><a href="http://www.chaosmystic.com/crimsonblade/"><font face="comic sans ms" color="crimson" size="1"><b>Crimson</b></font></a></td><td align=left bgcolor="#778899"><a href="http://www.chaosmystic.com/crimsonblade/"><font face="comic sans ms" color="crimson" size="1"><b> Blade </b></font></a></td></tr><tr><td align=middle colspan=3 bgcolor="#778899"><font face="comic sans ms" color="#003366" size="-1">Bursting forth with the power of ten <b>billion</b> <font color="#ff7777">b</font><font color="#ffff80">u</font><font color="#3ec0ff">t</font><font color="#ff75ff">t</font><font color="gold">e</font><font color="#ff75ff">r</font><font color="#3ec0ff">f</font><font color="#ffff80">l</font><font color="#ff7777">y</font> sneezes<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=558" target="_blank">My Magelo Profile</a> || <a href="http://www.phantommessenger.com/bamfort" target="_blank">My Homemade Profile</a></font></td></tr></table></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/udaleb123.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daleb123</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 58<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(5/14/02 7:39:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1499.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Damage Bonus</span><hr size=1> Maximum Damage is calculated by a formula that takes STR, weapon skill, ATK buffs (such as Wolf Form), and the Damage rating of the weapon into account.  Actual damage for any hit is then determined based on the Damage Mitigation of your opponent as well as a random factor. The Damage Bonus is then ADDED to the damage total for primary hand hits - IT DOES NOT ADD TO THE DAMAGE RATING OF THE WEAPON.<br>
<br>
For 1-handed weapons for all melee and hybrid classes, the Damage Bonus = (Level-25)/3, rounded down.<br>
<br>
For 2-handed weapons for all melee and hybrid classes, the Damage Bonus varies both by the Level of the wielder and by the Delay of the weapon (higher delay = higher bonus); I do not have a formula for you.<br>
<br>
I hope that helps. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/uyanbun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yanbun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(5/14/02 10:41:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1499.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> r</span><hr size=1> So my main hand min damage is 5, not 1? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/ubamfort.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bamfort</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.phantommessenger.com/bamfort/smyin.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br>  Posts: 727<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(5/14/02 11:45:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1499.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.phantommessenger.com/bamfort/pooh-zen.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Damage Bonus question</span><hr size=1> For your main hand, yes, your minimum damage is 5 at lvl 37.  Your <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> off-hand</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> is still 1, though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=1499.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showNextMessage?topicID=1499.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1499.topic&index=8><img 